		"description": "<p>You turn a creature's exhaustion into a well of inner strength. While under the effect of this spell, the target gains a number of temporary hit points equal to 1d6 &times; its combined levels of fatigue and strife at the start of each of its turns. Any temporary hit points remaining are lost when the spell ends.</p>\n<p>Additionally, if its total levels of fatigue and strife are 3 or more, the target gains advantage on its first attack roll each turn.</p>",
